OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has officially won the
OL,7,FMakerfield by election, but when he
OL,8,Ftakes his seat at Westminster, he will
OL,9,Fbe far from a newbie.
OL,11,FThe Greater Manchester mayor defeated
OL,12,FReform UK's Robert Kenyon by 9,231
OL,13,Fvotes, up from 5,399 in 2024, and
OL,14,FLabour's vote share increased by 9.61%.
OL,16,FOver the past two decades Burnham has
OL,17,Fclimbed the political ladder in
OL,18,FParliament, held ministerial roles in
OL,19,Ffour government departments and ran
OL,20,Ffor Labour leadership twice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
