OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FAll before resigning and returning his
OL,7,Fattention to the North where he has
OL,8,Fserved as Greater Manchester Mayor
OL,9,Fsince 2017.
OL,11,FLife before politics
OL,13,FAndy was born in Liverpool in 1970,
OL,14,Fhis father Kenneth was a BT engineer
OL,15,Fand his mother Eileen, a GP
OL,16,Freceptionist. He was one of three boys
OL,17,Fin a busy, Labour supporting
OL,18,Fhousehold, it was here that he
OL,19,Fdeveloped an interest in politics.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
