OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782139703
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FHe rose quickly through the ranks and
OL,7,Fsoon moved on to become special
OL,8,Fadviser to Culture Secretary Chris
OL,9,FSmith.
OL,11,FEntry to Westminster
OL,13,FBurnham was first elected as MP for
OL,14,FLeigh in 2001 and was introduced to
OL,15,FDowning Street as a junior Health
OL,16,FMinister under Tony Blair just four
OL,17,Fyears later.
OL,19,FFrom there, he joined Gordon Brown's
OL,20,Fcabinet as Chief Secretary to the
OL,21,FTreasury and later Culture Secretary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
