OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FThis paved the way for the formation
OL,7,Fof the Hillsborough Independent Panel,
OL,8,Fwhich would expose state corruption
OL,9,Fand a cover up by police to deflect
OL,10,Fblame onto Liverpool fans.
OL,12,FThe findings forced the prime minister
OL,13,Fto issue a formal apology and
OL,14,Fsuccessfully led to the 1991 inquest
OL,15,Fverdict of 'accidental death' being
OL,16,Fcompletely quashed.
OL,18,FIn 2016 a fresh inquest finally
OL,19,Fdeclared the 97 fans unlawfully killed.
OL,21,FLeadership elections
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
