OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor is an old
OL,7,Fhand at leadership contests too,
OL,8,Fhaving ran twice for the role more
OL,9,Fthan 10 years ago.
OL,11,FAfter Gordon Brown's resignation, in
OL,12,F2010 Burnham made his first bid for
OL,13,Fthe big job but was eliminated early
OL,14,Fon, finishing fourth out of five
OL,15,Fcandidates.
OL,17,FEd Milliband ultimately won, but
OL,18,FBurnham spent the next five years
OL,19,Fbuilding up his appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
