OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782139703
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FIn 2015, he tried again entering the
OL,7,Frace as the bookies favourite but was
OL,8,Fit wasn't to be, with Jeremy Corbyn
OL,9,Fwinning by a 59.5% landslide.
OL,11,FHe remained in Westminster for another
OL,12,Fyear as Shadow Home Secretary before
OL,13,Fresigning to become the Mayor of
OL,14,FGreater Manchester in 2017.
OL,16,FManchester Mayor
OL,18,FBurnham won the mayoral elections with
OL,19,Fmore than 60% of the vote.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
