OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FHis popularity hit its peak in 2020
OL,7,Fwhere he publicly took on Boris
OL,8,FJohnson over the decision to put
OL,9,FGreater Manchester into the highest
OL,10,Flevel of lockdown restrictions.
OL,12,FA huge point of contention was the
OL,13,Flack of financial support for low paid
OL,14,Fworkers, the stand-off earned him the
OL,15,Fnickname, 'King of the North'.
OL,17,FAnother success for Burnham was the
OL,18,Fintegration of Greater Manchester's
OL,19,Ftransport system to form 'The Bee
OL,20,FNetwork'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782139703
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FThis made Greater Manchester the first
OL,7,Fplace outside of London to bring bus
OL,8,Fservices and other modes of transport
OL,9,Ftogether and back under public control.
OL,11,FWhat's next?
OL,13,FNow Burnham has won the local
OL,14,Felection, he is free to place his bid
OL,15,Ffor party leadership.
OL,17,FIn the coming days, he will be sworn
OL,18,Fin as an MP in the House of Commons
OL,19,Fwhen he can then take up his seat.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
