OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FAfter that, it will be up to him and
OL,7,Fhis fellow Labour MPs over when to
OL,8,Ftrigger a leadership challenge.
OL,10,FFor a leadership election to be
OL,11,Ftriggered under Labour Party rules,
OL,12,F20% of the party's MPs (81 MPs
OL,13,Fcurrently) need to back a single
OL,14,Freplacement candidate first.
OL,16,FOnce that is done, the National
OL,17,FExecutive Committee, then arranges a
OL,18,Ftimetable for the election, which
OL,19,Fhistorically has varied significantly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
